<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="1015001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1015001"><g ref="#CB05849">󱛙</g>子＝迹于？</note>
<note n="1015002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1015002">千＝于？</note>
<note n="1015003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1015003">姓朴下見</note>
<note n="1015004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1015004">案當高麗高宗第二年。支那南宋寧宗嘉定八年。此傳之著蓋係此年</note>
<note n="1016001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1016001">續高僧傳卷八</note>
<note n="1016002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1016002">聖續傳作丞</note>
<note n="1016003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1016003">Asaṅga</note>
<note n="1016004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1016004">Vasubandhu</note>
<note n="1016005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1016005">三國遺事三注云。一作惠始</note>
<note n="1017001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017001">第十神異下</note>
<note n="1017002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017002">〔生〕－？</note>
<note n="1017003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017003">曰梁傳作於</note>
<note n="1017004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017004">Malananda</note>
<note n="1017005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017005">三國遺事卷三引百濟本記云第十五枕流王即位甲申難陀至注云僧傳云十四誤</note>
<note n="1017006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017006">拒＝距？</note>
<note n="1017007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017007">三國遺事卷三阿道下注云一作我道又阿頭</note>
<note n="1017008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1017008">三國遺事注云又作毛祿</note>
<note n="1018001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018001">三國遺事注云有注云與本碑及諸傳記殊異又高僧傳云西竺人或云從吳來</note>
<note n="1018002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018002">橋下遺事有東字</note>
<note n="1018003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018003">輪原本作輔今依下文法空傳及三國遺事改之</note>
<note n="1018004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018004">味遺事作未</note>
<note n="1018005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018005">村遺事作林注云今一善縣</note>
<note n="1018006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018006">三國遺事三注云祿與禮形近之誤</note>
<note n="1018007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1018007">興下原本空一字</note>
<note n="1019001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1019001">乎＝手？</note>
<note n="1019002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_1019002">年原本作梁今依下文覺德傳改之</note>
</p>
